#

Pork Vindaloo

$25
550 kcal

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freedairy-free

Tags:

Indian CuisinePorkSpicyAromatic

Description

A spicy and aromatic pork dish with a tangy kick, perfect for those who love bold flavors.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 2 lbs
  • Onions: 2 medium, sliced
  • Garlic: 6 cloves, minced
  • Ginger: 2 inches, minced
  • Vinegar: 1/2 cup
  • Brown sugar: 2 tbsp
  • Cumin seeds: 1 tsp
  • Coriander seeds: 1 tsp
  • Turmeric powder: 1 tsp
  • Red chili powder: 2 tbsp
  • Mustard seeds: 1 tsp
  • Bay leaves: 2
  • Salt: to taste
  • Oil: 3 tbsp
  • Water: as needed
